# StreamVault — UI Animation Overhaul

Integrate animated components from React Bits, Aceternity UI, Magic UI, Motion Primitives, and Cult UI across the entire StreamVault project. This replaces static UI elements with premium, animated alternatives.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Scope**: This touches **every page and component** in the project — 10+ files modified, 28+ new component files created. This will be done in 5 phases with verification after each.

> [!WARNING]
> **Breaking change — `framer-motion` → `motion`**: React 19 requires the new `motion` package (v12+), not the legacy `framer-motion`. All imports will use `motion/react` instead of `framer-motion`. This is the official successor.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Approach**: Since the CLI tools (`magicui-cli`, `jsrepo`, `shadcn`) may not work perfectly with Tailwind v4's new CSS-first config (no `tailwind.config.ts`), I will **manually create all components** by writing the source code directly, based on each library's open-source implementations. This avoids CLI compatibility issues entirely.

> [!NOTE]
> **DaisyUI co-existence**: All new animated components will use Tailwind utility classes + `motion` animations, which coexist perfectly with DaisyUI's `data-theme` system. No conflicts expected.

---

## Proposed Changes

### Phase 0: Foundation

#### [MODIFY] [package.json](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/package.json)
- Add `motion` (^12.34.0) as dependency
- Add `gsap` (~3.12) as dependency (for SplitText animation)

#### [MODIFY] [globals.css](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/app/globals.css)
- Add CSS keyframes for `shimmer`, `border-beam`, `aurora`, `meteor` animations
- These are pure CSS, no Tailwind config changes needed

---

### Phase 1: HomePage — Hero & Background

#### [NEW] [particles.tsx](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/components/ui/particles.tsx)
Interactive particle background using canvas + `motion`. Replaces [DotField](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/app/page.tsx#8-85) with configurable density, color, speed, mouse interactivity, and connecting lines.

#### [NEW] [blur-text.tsx](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/components/ui/blur-text.tsx)
Text animation that reveals each word/character with a blur-to-clear effect using `motion`. For the "StreamVault" headline.

#### [NEW] [shiny-text.tsx](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/components/ui/shiny-text.tsx)
CSS shimmer effect sweeping across text. Pure CSS keyframe animation — no JS runtime cost.

#### [NEW] [magnetic-button.tsx](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/components/ui/magnetic-button.tsx)
Button that follows cursor within a magnetic radius on hover using `motion`. For the hero CTA.

#### [NEW] [tilt-card.tsx](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/components/ui/tilt-card.tsx)
3D perspective tilt on hover using mouse position + CSS `transform: perspective() rotateX() rotateY()`. For feature cards.

#### [MODIFY] [page.tsx](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/app/page.tsx)
- Replace [DotField](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/app/page.tsx#8-85) with `Particles`
- Wrap hero heading in `BlurText`
- Wrap tagline in `ShinyText`
- Replace CTA button with `MagneticButton`
- Wrap feature cards in `TiltCard`

---

### Phase 2: Dashboard + Video Pages

#### [NEW] [number-ticker.tsx](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/components/ui/number-ticker.tsx)
Animated rolling number counter using `motion`. Counts up from 0 to target value when entering viewport.

#### [NEW] [animated-list.tsx](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/components/ui/animated-list.tsx)
Container that staggers children animation using `motion` `staggerChildren`. Video grid items fade+slide in sequentially.

#### [NEW] [spotlight-card.tsx](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/components/ui/spotlight-card.tsx)
Card container with a radial gradient spotlight that follows cursor position. For the video player wrapper.

#### [NEW] [border-beam.tsx](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/components/ui/border-beam.tsx)
Animated beam of light rotating around an element's border via CSS conic-gradient + keyframe. For quality badges.

#### [NEW] [text-effect.tsx](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/components/ui/text-effect.tsx)
Word-by-word or character-by-character entrance animation using `motion` variants. For video title/description.

#### [MODIFY] [page.tsx](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/app/dashboard/page.tsx)
- Wrap stat numbers in `NumberTicker`
- Wrap video grid in `AnimatedList`
- Add staggered card entrance

#### [MODIFY] [page.tsx](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/app/video/[id]/page.tsx)
- Wrap HLS player in `SpotlightCard`
- Wrap quality badges in `BorderBeam`
- Wrap title in `TextEffect`

---

### Phase 3: Upload + Auth Pages

#### [NEW] [file-upload-dropzone.tsx](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/components/ui/file-upload-dropzone.tsx)
Animated drag-and-drop zone with dotted border animation, file icon pulse, and smooth state transitions using `motion`.

#### [NEW] [shimmer-button.tsx](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/components/ui/shimmer-button.tsx)
Button with a sweeping shimmer light effect via CSS gradient animation. For Google Sign-In and primary CTAs.

#### [NEW] [confetti.tsx](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/components/ui/confetti.tsx)
Canvas-based confetti burst triggered on upload success. Lightweight, fires once and auto-cleans.

#### [NEW] [meteors.tsx](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/components/ui/meteors.tsx)
Animated meteor shower background using CSS animations. For login/register page backgrounds.

#### [NEW] [vanish-input.tsx](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/components/ui/vanish-input.tsx)
Input with cycling animated placeholder text that fades between hints. Submits with a vanish animation.

#### [MODIFY] [page.tsx](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/app/upload/page.tsx)
- Replace file input with `FileUploadDropzone`
- Add `Confetti` on successful upload
- Replace submit button with `ShimmerButton`

#### [MODIFY] [login-form.tsx](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/components/login-form.tsx)
- Add `Meteors` background
- Replace Google button with `ShimmerButton`

#### [MODIFY] [register-form.tsx](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/components/register-form.tsx)
- Add `Meteors` background
- Replace Google button with `ShimmerButton`

