#### [NEW] [gradient-text.tsx](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/components/ui/gradient-text.tsx)
Text with animated gradient that cycles through brand colors via CSS `background-clip: text` + keyframes.

#### [NEW] [glare-card.tsx](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/components/ui/glare-card.tsx)
Card with a shine/glare effect on hover using mouse-tracked radial gradient overlay.

#### [MODIFY] [header.tsx](file:///c:/Coding/media_streaming/components/header.tsx)
