## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- No existing test suite in the project. Adding unit tests is out of scope for this UI visual change.
- **Build check**: Run `npm run build` after each phase to catch TypeScript/compilation errors.

### Browser Verification (after each phase)
After completing each phase, I will visually verify in the browser at `http://localhost:3000`:

1. **Phase 1**: Navigate to `/` — confirm particles animate, hero text has blur-in, CTA has magnetic hover, feature cards tilt on hover
2. **Phase 2**: Navigate to `/dashboard` — confirm stat numbers count up, video cards stagger in. Navigate to `/video/{id}` — confirm spotlight, border beam, text reveal
3. **Phase 3**: Navigate to `/upload` — confirm dropzone animation, confetti on success. Navigate to `/login` and `/register` — confirm meteors, shimmer buttons
4. **Phase 4**: Confirm header gradient text, sidebar active indicator across all pages
5. **Phase 5**: Run `npm run build` for full production build check

### Manual Verification (for user)
After all phases, please manually check:
1. Open the app at `http://localhost:3000` and navigate through all pages
2. Verify animations are smooth and not janky
3. Verify DaisyUI themes still switch correctly (try 2-3 themes)
4. Verify all forms (login, register, upload) still function correctly
5. Verify video playback still works on the video player page
